<h1 align="center">&nbsp;<font size="7" face="Arial">Measurement for CBSE</font></h1>
<p>　</p>
<p><b><font face="Arial" size="6">What should I measure? </font></b></p>
<p><b><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font></b>
<font color=red>
<font face="Arial" size="6">1. Schedule (planned vs. actual)</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Commercial scheduling tools</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. Source instructions per 
component</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: .25in; margin-left: .75in">
  <font face="Arial" size="6">SLOC per component.</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. Labor hours</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  how much have done, not how many are working on it</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. Classification of the 
component</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  New code</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Changed code</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Built for reuse</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Reused code</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. Cost</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  $Cost/SLOC &nbsp; what's your bottom line?</font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. Change requests (CRs)</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Volatility of your component designs </font></li>
</ul>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7. Defects</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  Indicate the quality level of components</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  where in the life cycle you find the most defects and</font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  how much it costs to fix them</font></li>
</font>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .75in">　</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: .75in"><b><font face="Arial" size="6">
Technical measurements:</font></b></p>
<font color=red>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8. Time and quality for coding and design</font></p>
<p><font face="Arial" size="6">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 9. Response time and/or 
throughput</font></p>
<ul>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  CPU, memory and disk utilization </font></li>
  <li>
  <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in"><font face="Arial" size="6">
  how fast does the system run?</font></li>
</ul>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 1.0in">　</p>
<p>　</p>

